				<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p>Should we hide the TOC or try to restructure the template to get it to work with the TOC if possible or just leave as is? - <a href="http://wiki.osdev.org/User:Chase" title="User:Chase">Chase</a> 23:39, 11 December 2006 (CST)
